    "raw": "<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"kkp\">\n<style>\n.kkp{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto}\n.kkp .kkp-lead{font-size:1.18rem;line-height:1.5;max-width:62ch;margin:0 0 .4rem}\n.kkp .kkp-lead.kkp-kicker{font-weight:700}\n.kkp .kkp-label{font-size:.74rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;opacity:.55;margin:2rem 0 .85rem}\n.kkp .kkp-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(210px,1fr));gap:1rem}\n.kkp .kkp-card{display:block;border:1px solid rgba(150,150,160,.22);border-radius:11px;overflow:hidden;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;background:rgba(150,150,160,.05);transition:transform .15s ease,border-color .15s ease}\n.kkp .kkp-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:#e5462e}\n.kkp .kkp-card img,.kkp .kkp-ph{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;object-fit:cover;display:block}\n.kkp .kkp-ph{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#23232e 0%,#3a2230 100%)}\n.kkp .kkp-txt{padding:.7rem .8rem .85rem}\n.kkp .kkp-title{font-weight:700;font-size:.96rem;line-height:1.25}\n.kkp .kkp-sub{font-size:.8rem;opacity:.68;margin-top:.28rem;line-height:1.35}\n.kkp .kkp-cta{margin-top:2.4rem;padding-top:1.1rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(150,150,160,.22);font-size:1.02rem}\n.kkp .kkp-cta a{color:#e5462e;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none}\n.kkp .kkp-cta a:hover{text-decoration:underline}\n</style>\n\n<p class=\"kkp-lead kkp-kicker\">Most AI conversations force a binary.</p>\n<p class=\"kkp-lead\">Boosters say embrace it. Doomers say resist it. Both feel lazy. I hold the critique in one hand and the capability in the other. This is where I work through the hard parts. Power, bias, consent, sovereignty, and what we actually owe each other.</p>\n\n<div class=\"kkp-label\">Start here</div>\n<div class=\"kkp-grid\">\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/05/04/punk-rock-ai/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/kk-cmvan-keynote-header.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Punk Rock AI\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Punk Rock AI</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Holding the critique and the capability at once.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/02/03/name-the-bias/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/01-the-word-bias-dissolving.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Name the Bias\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Name the Bias</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Stop saying AI bias. Name what you're seeing.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/05/23/you-cant-drink-data/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/sign-01-fuck-ai.jpg?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"You Can't Drink Data\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">You Can't Drink Data</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Notes from my first anti-data-centre protest.</div></div></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"kkp-label\">Power, policy and sovereignty</div>\n<div class=\"kkp-grid\">\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/06/04/canada-ai-for-all-strategy-skeptical-guide/\"><div class=\"kkp-ph\"></div><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Canada's AI for All</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">A skeptical guide to the hype and the money.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/04/17/applied-ethical-ai-responsible-ai-professional-certification-rap/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/rap-faces.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Applied Ethical AI\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Applied Ethical AI</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Why we built the Responsible AI certification.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2024/09/12/ai-for-the-people-why-open-source-is-the-future-of-tech-sovereignty/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/MASTER-Blog-header-2.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"AI for the People\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">AI for the People</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Why open source is the future of tech sovereignty.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2024/11/22/great-creative-reckoning-a-techartists-manifesto-on-generative-artificial-intelligence/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"The Great Creative Reckoning\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">The Great Creative Reckoning</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">A techartist's manifesto on generative AI.</div></div></a>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"kkp-cta\">Browse the full <a href=\"https://kriskrug.co/category/ai-ethics-philosophy/\">AI Ethics and Philosophy</a> archive, or <a href=\"https://kriskrug.co/speaking/\">bring this conversation to your room</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->",
